                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1768" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0107</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8569 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张主任的得意之作——AHF公司现场布局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Director Zhang&#39;s Favorite Work——Facilities Layout of AHF Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郭强</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东方阿海珐核泵有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">布局；系统布置技术；产品流程程序</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">layout; system layout planning; product process procedure</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国制造经济的发展，现场设施布局已经成为一个企业界关注的热点问题。合理的生产车间设施布局是降低企业生产成本，提高生产效率，提升产品竞争力的重要因素之一。本案例以东方阿海珐核泵有限责任公司(AHF公司)为主要研究对象，探讨了该公司二期生产车间设施布局设计问题。
本案例首先依据现场调查分析，画出了公司的一期生产车间设施布局示意图，并总结性描述了一期车间因为设施布局不合理导致生产浪费的问题。同时，对其车间各个作业单元的进行了编号说明，标注其中不可移动的作业单元和二期车间需要布局的作业单元。最后，根据作业间单元物流与非物流关系，分别讨论两种情形下的布局问题，并叙述张主任采取的改善措施，合理规划出公司二期生产车间设施布局的初始方案。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of China&#39;s manufacturing economy, workshop facility layout has become a hot research topic. Reasonable workshop facility layout is one of the important factors to reduce production costs, increase productivity, improve product competitiveness. Currently, there are many domestic and foreign studies on large-scale manufacturing facility layout. This case takes Eastern Areva nuclear pump co, LTD（AHF company）as the main object of study, discusses the two phase of the production workshop facility layout problem.The case described production layout and technological process of the AHF company. We draw the schematic diagram of a company&#39;s production workshop facility layout and summarily described production of waste because of unreasonable planning of the first phase of the production workshop. Finally, according to the relationship between logistics and non logistics operation units, we put forward the layout problem of two kinds of circumstances. In this case, each work unit were numbered. Then we marked the unit which does not need to move the unit which needs to move in the layout of the second phase. Finally the case described that Mr.Zhang had been taken improvement measures, and how to plan the initial scheme of second production workshop facilities layout.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《生产运作管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">存货管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-11</td>
                            </tr>
